title: Career Counseling
description: Psychometric testing to find your Field of Interest and Skill Set to help you decide on the right Career Path

title: Education Counseling
description: Our Counselors receive extensive training to provide proper guidance in choosing the right field and level of study based on your Future Aspirations. Most of our counselors have been international students themselves and all have been trained abroad

title: Application Placement
description: Our dedicated Applications Team makes sure applications meet entry requirements, are placed properly, and that offers are received in a timely manner. We are a registered UCAS center and provide support with OUAC and Common App

title: University & Course Selection
description: Guidance in picking the right University based on academic qualification, budget, family circumstances, immigration plans, etc

title: Scholarships
description: We try our best to connect you with available scholarships to make study abroad more affordable. Many of our students receive scholarships for higher studie

title: Expert Visa Services
description: Our visa success is noteworthy as we have a dedicated Visa Team with vast experience and expertise.
